ddress":"","ucode":"79B45A1ABD077D","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/22/b0/56/d3216fe2.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1633341911,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1633341911","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"不经审视的人生不值得过，不经思考的知识不值得记。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":309503,"user_name":"不再是入门水平python的小宇","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2094450,"ip_address":"","ucode":"D49429660F2DC8","user_header":"http://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/S5RFBwro1nY4aRN2WkE08G9HicMTz1WzFm1PuHgRMYLbtMA4SZI7A127muWUVAV2CSpCMmHB64g9Zy8a1kVmRcg/132","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1630201532,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1630201532","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"我知道当年考研我为啥英语单词记不住了","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":308587,"user_name":"lee🙃","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1169467,"ip_address":"","ucode":"02E8C4C0B7CF40","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/d8/3b/b77b78c1.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1629691452,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1629691452","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"主动思考和加工：精细化提问<br>组块化记忆","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":305757,"user_name":"钱鹏 Allen","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2518863,"ip_address":"","ucode":"7E95E82C0717DA","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/26/6f/4f/3cf1e9c4.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1628150890,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1628150890","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"1.主动思考 我们在日常中所看的新闻，事件，深挖下去都可以组成我们的知识体系的<br><br>2.打包成组  大脑的单次输入的信息在5+-2之间，但我们可以形成知识结构，这个更符合大脑的神经结构","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":304689,"user_name":"You","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2662969,"ip_address":"","ucode":"ACBDB82E9B39C4","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/28/a2/39/3ee6f996.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1627550396,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1627550396","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"这一章可以说是结合了底层思维中：主动思考与主动加工中较为细节的操作。做到对知识点精细化提问，并且自己对这一提问做出主动思考与加工并且尝试给出答案。这就是记忆的思路与方向。再利用“组块化记忆”来对自己的主动思考过给出的答案的内容加以包装变成一个大的知识模块（知识体系）","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":301997,"user_name":"信仰年轻","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1329011,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B2BD881D25FCDD","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/47/73/63a3cb41.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1626013067,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1626013067","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"08｜高效记忆的根本方法：主动思考和加工 &amp; 组块化记忆<br><br>1.记忆的底层逻辑是主动思考+加工<br>2、组块化扩充。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":301005,"user_name":"海阔天空","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1551443,"ip_address":"","ucode":"C3711704A3637D","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/17/ac/53/ddbe4d80.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1625481970,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1625481970","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"大脑更容易记住的内容是符合自己习惯的语句，所以每一项新知识点多问自己一个“为什么”，用于自己的语言系统进行加工，形成符合自己记忆习惯的语句。<br>大脑一次短时记忆的容量是有限的，想要记住更多的内容，就需要浓缩一些零散的、相互独立的知识点（组块），把这些内容串联起来，形成一个组块，从而间接增加记忆的容量","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":299522,"user_name":"coder.js","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1338120,"ip_address":"","ucode":"3DE173A5D23690","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/6b/08/15c473ef.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1624694162,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1624694162","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"📒 笔记<br><br>“主动思考”和“加工”是可以应用在一切记忆场景中的。甚至可以认为，它们是记忆的底层逻辑。<br><br>## 主动思考&#47;加工<br><br>背单词，按部就班 ，难。<br><br>因为，大脑不擅长记忆无意义的东西。<br><br>&gt; 大脑能记住的，是“我们仔细思考过的东西”。  <br>&gt; ———— （美 威林厄姆《学生为什么不喜欢上学》）<br><br>根本 要义 是“主动”。<br><br>主动思考 🤔 ，主动仔细地思考，精细化地提问（elaborative interrogation）。<br><br>- 一个公式为什么会这样构成？<br>- 一个历史事件为什么发生在某个年份？<br>- 日本人是人吗？<br><br>这些问题并不需要正确地回答它，只是为了主动思考，帮助记忆。最后一个问题除外（ 🙃 ）。<br><br>&gt; 精细化提问，可以显著提高被试的学习和保持效果。  <br>&gt; ———— （美 苏珊·A·安布罗斯《聪明教学 7 原理》）<br><br>## 组块化记忆<br><br>什么是“组块”呢？组块是衡量记忆容量的一种单位。<br><br>一个数字，一个字母，一个单词，一个短语，一句诗，都是组块。<br><br>组块就是浓缩。在有限的 工作记忆（RAM），压缩知识，这样能装的就变多了。<br><br>### 例 1: 金庸<br><br>金庸的小说有：《射雕英雄传》《神雕侠侣》《倚天屠龙记》《天龙八部》《笑傲江湖》……<br><br>如果挨个记忆，很难。<br><br>但是换成 “飞雪连天射白鹿，笑书神侠倚碧鸳” ，就容易多了。<br><br>单独记忆每本书名，需要 14 个组块，记忆名字连成的诗只需要 2 个组块。<br><br>### 例 2 ：奇变偶不变，符号看象限<br><br>懂的都懂。<br>","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":298733,"user_name":"进化菌","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1276861,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B30A5F78BB4171","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/7b/bd/ccb37425.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1624281659,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":5,"score":"1624281659","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"记忆不谈技巧的话，大多是靠不断的重复。<br>高效记忆需要加点技巧了，比如联想记忆、理解记忆、归类记忆等等，这应该也都算是主动思考和加工吧？","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":298683,"user_name":"磉盘","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1055624,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1C245991F30A73","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/1b/88/ac69f57a.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1624262290,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1624262290","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"主动学习没问题，看视频学习肯定不如自己操作学习效率高。<br><br>这组块学习，金庸书名例子只能算是记忆口诀。组块记忆应该是分组记忆，比如把11位手机号分三组记忆。<br><br>又比如：鸡，苹果，鸭，香蕉，鱼，笔记本，猪，电视，狗。   如果直接记忆肯定困难，分组记忆就会简单。 这不应该是分组记忆吗？","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":298274,"user_name":"helloworld","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1105161,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1EECCA0F43E278","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/dd/09/feca820a.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1623994317,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"109016","content":"5-9个","user_name":